        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function doesn&apos;t assume anything concerning the status of the interrupts. Use <ref refid="group__mbox__interface_1ga9eea4b9501751919125cd6124f9e9868" kindref="member">mbox_set_enabled()</ref> to enable or to disable the interrupts if needed.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>dev</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>MBOX device instance </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>channel_id</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>MBOX channel identifier </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
