<para>Example devicetree fragment:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".devicetree"><codeline><highlight class="normal">n:<sp/>node<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>mboxes<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;&amp;mbox1<sp/>8&gt;,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;&amp;mbox1<sp/>9&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>mbox-names<sp/>=<sp/>&quot;tx&quot;,<sp/>&quot;rx&quot;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Example usage:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".c"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">const</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structmbox__dt__spec" kindref="compound">mbox_dt_spec</ref><sp/>spec<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="group__mbox__interface_1gadd0a5b06ab4b208460cf49952a2b4b43" kindref="member">MBOX_DT_SPEC_GET</ref>(<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-id_1gab7d23294a6bf7fd44a98b48ec47d8a79" kindref="member">DT_NODELABEL</ref>(n),<sp/>tx);</highlight></codeline>
